section.def:
fish
                (魚、魚類) means
            any marine fish, crustacean or mollusc, other than an oyster;

licence
                (牌照) means a licence granted or renewed under
                section 8;

permit
                (許可證) means a permit granted or renewed under
                section 14;

site
                (場地) means a site within a fish culture zone
            specified under section 5(b);

subparagraph.content:
committed for the purposes of or in
                        connexion
                        with fish culture operations;
